Be the change you wish to see in your feed.
NYC based. Creating worldwide.
Founder @from.label 🌿

posts.caption: Sunglasses and coffee cos this jet lag got my circadian rhythm outta whack. Playing catch up and running errands all day. I used to never get jet lag this bad. Does it get worse as you get older? Any jet lag cures send my way please ❤️ I’ll love ya forever.
Thank you, next meal please. Because all I’ve been doing is eat these past 2 days. 😂 #travelblogger #blogger #lightroompresets #paris

Running errands usually means doing one errand, coffee and a few hours at Target. 😂 But today it’ll be actual errands + I’ll be inserting a stop to see my boo @scottsinnyc because my hair needs some lovin before the holidays. Also what should I bring to my holiday potlucks? Suggestions?

[ R E A D ] And just like that the weekend’s done! Flew home right in time for this weekend’s closet sale. Huge thanks to you who came and stopped by today. Meeting you guys means so much to me! To be completely honest I am V tired. After nonstop traveling for 2+ months, working my butt off etc, I think it wouldn’t hurt to take my shoes off, brain off and lay back for the rest of today.✨ we are human and if each billion of cells in our body works just as hard as us, I think they deserve some love back, don’t you? ❤️ Have a great rest of your Sunday! #selflove #breaktime

As I was washing the dishes this morning (yes we don’t do maids and coming from the Philippines oddly enough I never trusted dish washers lol), I had a thought.
•

Here’s a confession. Half the time you see my power posts: blazer, bold brow, computer in one hand and inserted powerful feminist quote surrounding all sorts of yes we cans. (Don’t get me wrong, yes we sure can!) but what you don’t see is, behind those photos, is a girl just like you. •

I never have it “on” 23/7. I have vegetative days where I look for my phone, forgetting I’m holding it. Or get super anxious when I’m juggling a thousand things all with the same deadlines. Never wanna get out of bed, stay in sweats, repeat the same outfit to meetings with zero shame. Compare my work with others and become my biggest critic ~ ever. I am that person. •

A reminder that no human is on all the time. Hence why we are called humans. We can only give it our best and then balance it with a nice few hours away from our work, a few hours being kinder to yourself and dive into a pedicure or something like that. ❤️🥰 #bloggerstyle #greylayers #hustle #lightroompresets

Post thanksgiving mood tbh. On our way to chop down this year’s tree! I’ve never done this before. We usually just use a faux one or buy a real one off a tree store. Soooo I am Really excited!! 🤗 Follow along on my stories! Anyone have any fave holiday activities? 🌲✨ #holiday #christmasdecor
Black Friday is cute but so is coffee, Netflix and getting my nails done with zero wait time. 💆🏻‍♀️🤷🏻‍♀️. Who went shopping? Any good deals? Who stayed away from it? I wanna hear from you. ❤️

It’s the littlest things sometimes. HBU? •
-For a few more hours in bed.
-conversations that go for 5+ hours that make me forget about my phone.
-Pets’ undying love for you no matter what.
-The feeling of coming home every time I visit a new place in the world.
-The first drop of temperature change in the fall.
-Baby animals
-$5 Movie Tuesdays at AMC’s everywhere.
-For Spotify’s Deep Focus and Totally stress free playlists.•
-strength through these years.
-Learning to master loving and accepting myself.
-My parents Who feel like my friends when conversed with.•
-Each of your 472k selves who help unknowingly pick me up every single day.
- Friends who laugh just as hard as I do •
-This life and everything it’s given me.
✨What are you thankful for?✨

Finally woke up from my Instagram slumber. What’d I miss? 😂 Growth also comes from rest and energy cleansing. I took a 3 day IG cleanse and spent it with family. Cool to hang with people who make you forget about your phone. ❤️ #newyork

So fresh and ready to get lit. First time going to a farm and cutting our own tree! The struggle in our stories 🤗. Now for some hot cocoa. Officially 1 month before my favorite holiday! #christmas #holiday #newyork
Been around the world but there’s nothing quite like home 🗽. Where are you from?

[ A few new people here so I thought I’d do this ] share something about yourself too 🥰 •
- Hi I’m Jeanne.
- My real name is not @thegreylayers.
- If we’re super close, you’ll call me Teej.
- Iced latte with oat milk only.
- Movies over tv shows.
- I still bop to 90’s RnB and HipHop like they just got released today.
- I love social media but I love my private life more.
- I am an outfit repeater and usually live in the same exact outfit for 1 week straight. •
- I buy about 5 of the same items when I shop.
- I can’t do yoga.
- I can’t do without acupuncture. •
- INFP, Aquarius, moon in Scorpio
- Spends a ton on leggings, sweats and sleeping clothes but would think twice on designer things.
